{"tid":918840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本下月公布新版防衛計畫大綱 傳將增購百架F-35 加賀號、出雲號改造成航空母艦","createTime":"2018-11-27T14:11:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-29T02:34:13.000Z","uid":28765,"like":18,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"330a600ef6fd665b92c2dc7e7d9dbe38791a0d7c","tid":918840,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:11:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/article/20181127160029237316.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Farticle%2F20181127160029237316.jpg&h=99060eec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本政府考慮再增購百架F-35戰機，強化自身國防能力。（圖片取自航空自衛隊）<br />\n戰後由美軍主導、於1947年5月3日頒布施行的《日本國憲法》實行至今已71年。<br />\n當年盟軍為斬斷任何軍國主義崛起的機會，透過憲法第九條限制，不讓日本擁有「正規軍隊」、而僅有被動防禦權力的自衛隊，使日本進入有別戰前的和平憲法時代。<br />\n比照北約調高軍費<br />\n 《產經新聞》26日報導，新版《防衛計畫大綱》即將出爐，數名不具名日本政府官員向媒體透露，首相安倍晉三（Shinzo Abe）迫於美國總統川普（Donald Trump）的壓力，決定將現有佔國內生產總值（GDP）0.9%的軍費，比照北大西洋公約組織（NATO）規定，調昇為1.3%的比例。<br />\n向美增購百架F-35戰機<br />\n 《日經亞洲評論》（Nikkei Asia Review）更直指，安倍政府有意編列1兆日圓（約新台幣2700億）、再「增購」100架F-35戰機，除了先前42架、作為替換老舊F-4J「幽靈」戰機（F-4 Phantom II）之用外。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/photo01.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2Fphoto01.jpg&h=3e2a2501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n急於找到繼任者的日本F-4J「幽靈」戰機。（圖片取自航空自衛隊）<br />\n 現有200架F-15「鷹式」戰機（F-15 Eagle）的日本，半數機種在無法更新升級下，將用新採購的F-35戰機替換，而新訂單也不再侷限於傳統A型，能短場起降的B型也列入選項之一。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/photo02_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2Fphoto02_1.jpg&h=dcf951ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本現役兩架F-15J「鷹式」戰機。（圖片取自航空自衛隊）<br />\n安倍向川普低頭？<br />\n 此報導一出，立刻引發日本媒體正反兩極的討論和爭論。<br />\n報導中更提到，安倍政府決議向美國加購F-35B型戰機（F-35 Lightning II），似乎是真的有意將海上自衛隊（JMSDF）現役的「加賀號」護衛艦（JS Kaga）或同級的出雲號（JS Izumo）改造升級，強化甲板的厚度與耐熱力，讓加賀號的規格朝向正規航空母艦精進。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/183_04l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2F183_04l.jpg&h=ac0a7137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本現役出雲號護衛艦。（圖片取自海上自衛隊）<br />\n對此採購案，《讀賣新聞》卻認為，戰機價格極度不透明、又是為了「說服」川普，以此抵銷美日貿易赤字而買，恐怕難以得到民眾的支持。<br />\n除此之外，現階段曝光的計畫內容，還包含間諜衛星、陸基版導彈防空系統（Aegis BMD）、強化離島防衛等，主要的「假想敵」依然是暗藏野心的北韓與中國。<br />\n然而外界最關注的加賀號改造計畫，受限於憲法第九條條文、目前只有被動防衛權的日本，先不論其經費、技術和時間問題，將「護衛艦」變更為戰鬥用的航空母艦，恐怕就已是違反憲法規定。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/184_05l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2F184_05l.jpg&h=cfe98cfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本現役加賀號護衛艦。（圖片取自海上自衛隊）<br />\n 一旦安倍政府確定要這麼做，必將引來中國方面的激烈抗議和反擊，屆時關係本就曖昧的中日兩國，很可能又將陷入一場難解的對峙局面。<br />\n昂貴的第五代匿蹤戰機<br />\n F-35匿蹤戰機，由國防大廠洛克希德馬丁（Lockheed Martin），聯手諾格（Northrop Grumman）、普惠（Pratt &amp; Whitney）和英國航太系統（BAE），加上美國等11國合資，以聯合攻擊戰鬥機計劃（Joint Strike Fighter program）進行研發製造。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%E4%BB%A3F-35%E5%8C%BF%E8%B9%A4%E6%88%B0%E6%A9%9F%E6%80%A7%E8%83%BD%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9%E6%AF%94%E8%BC%83%E8%A1%A8_2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2F%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%2594%25E4%25BB%25A3F-35%25E5%258C%25BF%25E8%25B9%25A4%25E6%2588%25B0%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%2580%25A7%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2594%25AE%25E5%2583%25B9%25E6%25AF%2594%25E8%25BC%2583%25E8%25A1%25A8_2.jpg&h=4721480b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本目前擁有傳統空軍的A型戰機，而媒體傳聞的B型、屬於能短場起降（short take-off and vertical landing, STOVL）的F-35B型戰機，能擔負尺寸較小的軍艦艦載任務，現駐紮在日本的美軍胡蜂號兩棲突襲艦（USS Wasp ,LHD 1），艦上就有搭載該類戰機。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/6209085833_a516631032_b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2F6209085833_a516631032_b.jpg&h=c5c70de9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n能短場/垂直起降的F-35B戰機，也一直是日本政府考慮購買的型號之一。（圖片取自美國海軍）<br />\n修改憲法有可能實施？<br />\n事實上，安倍晉三和新任防衛大臣岩屋毅（Takeshi Iwaya）10月在東京朝霞基地校閱自衛隊時，致辭演說中就已提及《防衛計畫大綱》。<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/upload/ck/AP18322151488393.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fupload%2Fck%2FAP18322151488393.jpg&h=642af038&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n12月公佈新版《防衛計畫大綱》，安倍晉三（圖右）是否會追加修憲選項，也倍受關注。（美聯社）<br />\n「過去5年來，（由於中國崛起和北韓問題）讓日本的國家安全出現高度不確定性，這是件急迫且棘手的事情。12月將公佈的新《防衛計畫大綱》，我們將優先鞏固未來數十年防衛能力的基礎建設，專注於航太、電磁波和網際網路等新興領域研發工作，才能確保日本在全球的優勢地位。」<br />\n此番新版防衛計畫頒布，外界都在關注、安倍究竟會不會堅持，藉由凍結或廢止「第九條」，讓日本能名正言順地發展國防武力和恢復正規軍隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=52986\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.upmedia.mg%2Fnews_info.php%3FSerialNo%3D52986&d=CXCMuuhwcMS%2FMedlsEZQisVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=21213bf4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.upmedia.mg/news_info.php?SerialNo=52986</a>"},{"pid":"190c503f84c136e37c99a8d1b65e39115e8dbd47","tid":918840,"uid":54481,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"說好的軍用比民用領先幾代.....<br />\n點解仲買F-35<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542797189_5f96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542797189_5f96.jpg&h=672bd395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1:1可動高達RX-78-2將會按照設定高18米，是來自Gundam Global Chellenge計劃，此劃是集合各方意見，實現原大可動高達的夢想企劃，現在預定2020年季，於日本橫濱Gundam Factory Yokohama展示製作成果。"},{"pid":"491c4f3b0fcec8ba1537f4c1db428bc7e0dde32d","tid":918840,"uid":85659,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"190c503f84c136e37c99a8d1b65e39115e8dbd47","tid":918840,"uid":54481,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:14:38.000Z","msg":"說好的軍用比民用領先幾代.....<br />\n點解仲買F-35<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181121/large/1542797189_5f96.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181121%2Flarge%2F1542797189_5f96.jpg&h=672bd395&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1:1可動高達RX-78-2將會按照設定高18米，是來自Gundam Global Chellenge計劃，此劃是集合各方意見，實現原大可動高達的夢想企劃，現在預定2020年季，於日本橫濱Gundam Factory Yokohama展示製作成果。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a017f91cfd3174943fe77b27b3d719d263ebf70","tid":918840,"uid":141151,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:18:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大量F35-B"},{"pid":"37793c79650ac7d328ff017e2a65a92832fa0f9c","tid":918840,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:22:51.000Z","msg":"交保護費即."},{"pid":"06cb9eebac49e569cfd21b623abdf0a0876cb779","tid":918840,"uid":31151,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T14:24:13.000Z","msg":"首相安倍晉三（Shinzo Abe）迫於美國總統川普（Donald Trump）的壓力，決定將現有佔國內生產總值（GDP）0.9%的軍費，比照北大西洋公約組織（NATO）規定，調昇為1.3%的比例。<br />\n<br />\n人地幫你炸 你唔加軍費買撚得起咁多f35咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca2792acb508b343cdcbb23da10ae58e153c08ec","tid":918840,"uid":58552,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:11:10.000Z","msg":"強國勃起要開打 第一個一定打日本<br />\n復仇主義"},{"pid":"f02f65989a7876f2d168fba975a9aa02a26231be","tid":918840,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-27T15:13:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/0O2zyIoNNPM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F0O2zyIoNNPM&d=CXCMuuhwcMS%2FMedlsEZQisVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=efed4ea5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/0O2zyIoNNPM</a><br />\n請配合此BGM服用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1754ae8ae2f1524d